data.title: "Inspector Mista" Khust (TV Episode 2016)
data.meta_description: Khust: With Olga Freymut. The largest inspections of cities begins with a small town on the border with Europe - Khust. The viewers very were asking to inspect the local maternity hospital, which is why the inspector started with it. Bribes, cockroaches, unsanitary rooms, and find out what else is the medical institution hiding. We will tell you how the mayor and his wife live and visit the honored Ukrainian teacher to find out what's really hiding her smile.
